{"tid":45820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DBS即時關閉出賣客戶資料部門","createTime":"2016-12-19T08:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T14:08:48.000Z","uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d2a18d3cd7900a965a3a8751f2de9796a4791a","tid":45820,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"星展香港早前有職員涉受賄，出售客戶資料予內地電話中心，進行非法電話促銷活動，多名現任及前任員工被廉署拘捕，有報導引述市民消息謂，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">該行今日關閉其毋抵押貸款直銷業務，部門相關員工全部離職</span></span>。星展香港發言人回覆本報證實，毋抵押貸款直銷業務部門，已即時關閉，但未有透露多少員工受影響離職，亦無詳述當中是否有委託第3方中介銷售。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該行有關部門員工少於100人，當中有部份員工為委託中介。"},{"pid":"6e9786b7a6fb19c10b541cda9dbca796d7bb2287","tid":45820,"uid":11034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"原來係依班仆街，唔怪得知我姓乜#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"6576d2c39aac0e12801ceeeaa10820bebe2a876c","tid":45820,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"其實點止星展呀"},{"pid":"e7ff82f42c070ddb5fb498b75d446f123c735aa3","tid":45820,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:43:11.000Z","msg":"銀行狗明明就係比上面班垃圾逼跑數,出事比人拉,沒事又比人炒"},{"pid":"cd9768fd9a527d7629929983428275e4e5733611","tid":45820,"uid":28878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"有無得追討賠償？"},{"pid":"5ceb03ffedb3d764355f6e020897313dca3af412","tid":45820,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無得追討賠償？</blockquote><br />\n就係特登摺左佢然後銷毀晒D證據，等你無得告"},{"pid":"8b1cf60a2d233bf507690657469fcd2d2b3f53ab","tid":45820,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>銀行狗明明就係比上面班垃圾逼跑數,出事比人拉,沒事又比人炒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係，過橋抽板食哂死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7c31c2bba56